==投球風格==
弗恩特斯是一位左手[[低肩側投|低肩側投]]投手，主要球種為[[滑球|滑球]]和[[變速球|變速球]]。雖然他的球速不是很頂尖但是放球點位子拿捏得宜，球在出手時會有飄浮感，常常讓打者打擊時失去平衡。很多左打者表示感覺弗恩特斯的球彷彿是從他的袖子後面飛過來。

==私人生活==
弗恩特斯來自一個墨西哥裔美國籍家庭<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.newamericamedia.org/news/view_article.html?article_id=3b2642696eb2ea042bf37b8cf0edbefd |title=Santana and 'Big Papi' Lead Latino Baseballers |date=2007-04-02 |accessdate=2009-10-29 |author=Ray Estrada |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017024602/http://news.newamericamedia.org/news/view_article.html?article_id=3b2642696eb2ea042bf37b8cf0edbefd |archivedate=2013-10-17 }}</ref>，他和妻子芭芭拉擁有四個孩子，最大的叫吉奧瓦尼，老二和老三是雙胞胎，分別是兒子貝內西奧和女兒加布里拉，最小的孩子叫法拉<ref>{{cite web | url = http://losangeles.angels.mlb.com/team/player.jsp?player_id=150118 | title = Brian Fuentes Stats, Bio, Photos, Highlights | accessdate = 2009-10-29 | work = [[MLB.com|MLB.com]] | archive-date = 2010-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100119212241/http://losangeles.angels.mlb.com/team/player.jsp?player_id=150118 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_6913712 | title = Young pitchers look like keepers for 2008 | work = 丹佛郵報 | date = 2007-09-17 | accessdate = 2009-10-29 | author = Patrick Saunders | archive-date = 2008-07-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080709042252/http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_6913712 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他們賽季休息期住在弗恩特斯的老家美熹德。


